</style><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="7kYNsBQNpj"><a href="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-resource-center-officially-name-nintendo-museum/">任天堂博物馆的正式名称（暂定名）已确定为“任天堂博物馆”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“任天堂博物馆（暂定名）的正式名称已确定为“任天堂博物馆”” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-resource-center-officially-name-nintendo-museum/embed/#?secret=DBaD3JWXs2#?secret=7kYNsBQNpj" data-secret="7kYNsBQNpj" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="mq1Hl7umYJ"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-announces-retirement-of-mario-voice-actor-charles-martinet-and-appointment-as-goodwill-ambassador/">任天堂宣布退休并任命马里奥配音演员查尔斯·马丁内特亲善大使</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“任天堂宣布马里奥配音演员查尔斯·马丁内特退休并任命为亲善大使” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-announces-retirement-of-mario-voice-actor-charles-martinet-and-appointment-as-goodwill-ambassador/embed/#?secret=NrGg7VDAUU#?secret=mq1Hl7umYJ" data-secret="mq1Hl7umYJ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/release/2023/230919.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="京都四条通地下通道上张贴的描绘“超级马里奥”世界的图形">京都四条通地下通道上张贴的描绘“超级马里奥”世界的图形</a></p><cite>任天堂</cite></blockquote><p>（<em>文章由 P2y.jp 游戏/任天堂类别分发</em>）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-to-permanently-display-graphics-depicting-the-world-of-super-mario-in-kyoto-shijo-dori-underpass/">任天堂帖子首次出现在 P2y.jp 上</a><